01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 ngay v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_41687\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/phong-ngu.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41687\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/phong-ngu.jpg\" alt=\"V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e8n led m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1ed7ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e8n led m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1ed7ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_41689\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/Co-su-ho-tro-cua-den-led-thi-bo-giuong-ngu-don-dieu-cua-gia-dinh-cung-tro-nen-thu-hut-den-bat-ngo_2.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-41689\" src=\"http:\/\/kientrucvietnam.org.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/Co-su-ho-tro-cua-den-led-thi-bo-giuong-ngu-don-dieu-cua-gia-dinh-cung-tro-nen-thu-hut-den-bat-ngo_2.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e8n led \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba kh\u00f4ng l\u00f3a m\u1eaft, v\u1eeba \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5m c\u00fang h\u01a1n cho kh\u00f4ng gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i ri\u00eang t\u01b0 n\u00e0y\" width=\"567\" height=\"794\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"wp-capti